data.description: Calling all investors or savvy home buyers. Priced well below recent appraisal. This fixer upper is a solid, well built, custom home on 5 acres! The private setting is unbelievable! This home is 3869 sq feet and has 4 bedrooms, several flex/bonus spaces, 3 full bathrooms, and 3 half baths. The unique floorpan provides ample room for everyone including an entire apartment upstairs, complete with a 2nd kitchen and laundry. 2 storage buildings included. Enjoy privacy and wildlife in this peaceful retreat. Whitesburg-Central-Central school district. Buyer encouraged to complete due diligence prior to making an offer. No contingencies or assignment contracts.
